{"product_id":"regular-cropped-tee-drip-surf","title":"REGULAR CROPPED TEE - DRIP SURF","description":"\u003cp\u003e240 GSM. Premium Fabric. Minimal Design. 100% Combed Cotton. Gender-Neutral. Regular-Fit Cropped Silhouette. Relaxed Waist. Combed \u0026amp; Bio-washed.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis premium 240 GSM cropped T-shirt from Drip Studios is designed for effortless everyday wear. Crafted with a clean, minimal aesthetic, it features a regular fit with a relaxed waistline that offers comfort without compromising structure. The cropped length adds a modern edge, making it easy to style across casual and elevated looks. Made from combed and bio-washed cotton, this tee delivers a soft hand feel, breathability, and long-lasting durability. A versatile essential built for comfort, balance, and timeless appeal.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eProducts in lighter shades (such as white or off-white) are \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cstrong data-start=\"60\" data-end=\"99\"\u003enot eligible for return or exchange\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cspan\u003e due to the high risk of stains, discoloration, or signs of use during handling or trial. Customers are advised to review product details carefully before placing an order for these colors.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eMachine wash the T-shirt inside out with similar colors. Use cold water to maintain fabric quality. Tumble dry on low heat or air dry to avoid shrinkage. Store in a cool, dry place to preserve the fabric.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCore Features\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e240 GSM fabric for a lightweight yet premium feel. Regular-fit cropped design with a relaxed waist for easy movement and comfort. Gender-neutral silhouette suitable for diverse body types. Soft, breathable combed cotton ensures all-day wearability. Bio-washed finish for enhanced durability a\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"DRIPDRIP","offers":[{"title":"S","offer_id":475001